msquerybuilderbackend.entity

Class QueryBuilderJsonStringObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • msquerybuilderbackend.entity.QueryBuilderJsonStringObject

  • public class QueryBuilderJsonStringObject
extends java.lang.Object
    entity class of QueryBuilderJsonStringObject (for the backend and neo4j database) with getter and setter QueryBuilderJsonStringObject is an entity used only in the backend and neo4j database the entity is relevant for saving the QueryBuilder object as JSONString to keep all details and hierarchies because saving it as a QueryBuilder object in the neo4j database would mean that not all dependencies would be saved when there are many levels in the hierarchy
    Author:
    drago
